  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Characterization Study of Colombian Population in Ecuador 2020</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Colombian consulate in Quito, under its &#x201C;Colombia Nos Une&#x201D; Program, has identified the need for an exercise in the identification, location and profiling of Colombian migration, in recognition of the validity and permanence of these flows, as well as their diverse profiles that on many occasions they are not visible. A desk study on the Colombian population in Ecuador will be performed along with a citizen mapping on the dynamics of the Colombian population in Ecuador in Quito, Guayaquil, and Santo Domingo de los Ts&#xE1;chilas. The project will construct the data profiling and measurement tool and its enabling of a web platform.</narrative>
  </description>
